def get_avg(frame: IntoDataFrameT, by: str, agg: str) -> IntoDataFrameT:
    return (
        nw.from_native(frame)
        .group_by(by)
        .agg(nw.col(agg).mean())
        .sort(agg, descending=True)
        .to_native()
    )
